Case 1:20-cr-00330-PAE Document 747 Filed 08/10/22 Page 140 of 228 816 LC2VMAX4 Alessi - Direct
1 Q. Mr. Alessi, are you saying that the majority of the items on page 29 were not in the booklet that Ms. Maxwell gave you?
2 A. Yes.
3 Q. Were some of the items on page 29 in the booklet that Ms. Maxwell gave you?
4 A. Yes, but I -- yes.
5 Q. Let's go to page 30.
6 A. The same thing in this page. Some of the stuff I don't remember purchasing or seeing it before.
7 Q. But were some of them in the booklet that you remember Ms. Maxwell giving you?
8 A. Yes.
9 Q. Let's go to page 31.
10 A. Same thing.
11 Q. Same thing?
12 A. Same thing. These items -- some of these items I -- I never -- I was never given this list of shopping.
13 Q. But are there some items on here that you remember from a page --
14 A. Yes.
15 Q. -- in a booklet that Ms. Maxwell gave you?
16 A. Absolutely. Except for the liquor.
17 Q. Please don't describe the content of the document.
18 Let's go to page 32.
19 A. Yes.
SOUTHERN DISTRICT REPORTERS, P.C. (212) 805-0300
